<H3>JAMES A. PHILLIPS</H3>
<HR>
<B>SENIOR POLICY ANALYST, MIDDLE EASTERN AFFAIRS</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/phillips.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
