<HTML>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<TITLE>DAVID MASON -- Heritage </TITLE>
<H3>
DAVID MASON</H3>
<HR>
<B>VICE PRESIDENT, GOVERNMENT RELATIONS</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/mason.jpe" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
Mason studies the problems that critics say have left Congress unresponsive to the taxpayers and beholden to special interests.  Under his direction, Heritage published The Ruling Class: Inside the Imperial Congress (1993), an assessment of pervasive institutional problems and solutions. He also directed Heritage's liaison program with the executive branch, and identified and recommended conservative candidates for key public policy positions. A former Deputy Assistant Secretary of Defense  and  eight-year  veteran  of  Capitol  Hill,  Mason  previously served as Staff Director to then-House Minority Whip Rep. Trent Lott, R-Miss.

<BR><HR WIDTH="30%"><BR><CENTER><A HREF="/heritage/hbut.map"><IMG SRC="/heritage/hbut.gif" ISMAP BORDER=0></A></CENTER></BODY>
</HTML>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT17-B03-26</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA025-000260-B047-18</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
