<html>
<title>About the Job Bank - Heritage</title>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">

<CENTER>

<table border=10><tr><td valign="top">
<h2><center>The Heritage Foundation<br>
Job Bank</center></h2>
</td></tr></table>
<h3>A <I>FREE</I> Service Available to Washington-Area Employers</h3></center>
<p>

<center><h3>Job Bank Mission</h3></center>
The goal of the Heritage Job Bank, founded in 1980, is to assist in the placement of conservatives in public policy-related positions, both in the legislative and executive branches and in the private sector.
<p>
Recognizing that people are policy, the Job Bank seeks to place qualified individuals with conservative credentials in key policy-making or support positions in Congress, trade associations, policy institutions, the media, and elsewhere. The Job Bank is also committed to developing a long-term working relationship with Washington-area employers. 
<p>
Our candidate placement process is CONFIDENTIAL and discreet for both employer and employee. We are sensitive to the needs to both the candidate and employer and match the candidate's abilities with the specific requirements of the prospective employer.



<P>
<img src="/heritage/jobs/check.gif"><b>Our Business is PERSONNEL.</b>
<p>
The Heritage Foundation Job Bank promotes conservative policy through personnel.
<p>
<img src="check.gif"><b>Our Mission is QUALITY.</b>
<p>
We are committed to providing you with the highest quality conservative candidates possible. We select only candidates who can work and communicate effectively with others.
<p>
<img src="check.gif"><b>We are FAST AND EFFICIENT.</b>
<P>
We expedite the search process for you by providing resumes within twenty-four hours.
<p>
<img src="check.gif"><b>Our Service is FREE.</b>
<p>
It costs you absolutely nothing to request and receive quality resumes for your opening. We save you time and money. Compare our free service with area placement and recruitment agencies.
<p>
<img src="check.gif"><b>Our Candidate Pool is DIVERSE.</b>
<p>
We meet your job needs. We have qualified candidates who are experienced in a variety of fields, with varying experience levels, from entry- and mid-level to senior executive positions.
<p><center><hr width=50%></center>
<p>
<i><b>"The quality of the resume bank and professionalism of the Heritage staff made the difference 
for us in locating the right person for the job."</b></i>
<P>
-- April McKinney<br>
Office of Majority Leader Dick Armey, <br>
U.S. House of Representatives
<p>
<i><b>"Heritage's Job Bank gives a candidate instant credibility within a highly competitive field."</b></i>
<p>
-- Amy Bocklage White<br>
Office of Senator John Ashcroft
<p>

<i><b>"The Heritage Foundation recommended a perfect match for our needs.  It provided a hardworking and responsible individual with impressive credentials."
</b></i>
<p>
-- Jenny Byler<br>
The Marketing Department, Inc.
<p>
<i><b>"The Heritage Job Bank has been a tremendous resource...a great source for qualified applicants. We've enjoyed using the Job Bank for years." 
</b></i>
<p>
-- Ed Stong<br>
U.S. English  
<p>
<i><b>"The people we interviewed from Heritage's Job Bank were all very knowledgeable about petroleum issues.  We were very impressed with the quality
of the candidates."</b></i>
<p>
-- Liz Proutt<br> 
National Petroleum Refiners Association
<p>
<hr><p>

