<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/discovery/jewish.html 204.71.237.73 19970108190623 text/html 6343
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 19:06:29 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:30:46 GMT
