HEIGHT="68" ALIGN="MIDDLE" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A> <A HREF="current.html"><IMG SRC=
"image45.gif" WIDTH="156" HEIGHT="68" ALIGN="MIDDLE" NATURALSIZEFLAG="0"></A>
